Usage: create_proto_model [-help] [-keep_inst_file <string>] [ [-out_dir <string>] [-module_model_tag <string>] ]

-help                                      # Prints out the command usage
-keep_inst_file <string>                   # Specified instances in this file
                                           # will be kept. (string, optional)
-module_model_tag <string>                 # Create flexmodel based on ART,
                                           # output into SHDB (string, optional)
-out_dir <string>                          # Create flexmodel based on ART.
                                           # (string, optional)